  <brief_title>Interest of ß 1-3 D Glucan Assays in Screening for the Onset of Invasive Aspergillosis in Neutropenic Patients With Acute Leukaemia.</brief_title>
  <acronym>BETA GLUCAN</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective Study on the Interest of ß 1-3 D Glucan Assays in Screening for the Onset of Invasive Aspergillosis in Neutropenic Patients With Acute Leukaemia.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
