    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Centre Hospitalier Universitaire Dijon</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In the context of screening for infectious fungal diseases in patients with malignant
      haemopathy, and particularly patients with acute leukaemia, the investigator aims to evaluate
      the performance of an already commercialized but little used serum screening test (Fungitell®
      test) and to determine its place in the management strategy for invasive aspergillosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
