  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who have been informed about the study

          -  Patients over 18 years

          -  patients with acute myeloblastic leukaemia (AML) or lymphoblastic leukaemia (ALL) who
             have undergone cytotoxic chemotherapy with curative intent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Adults under guardianship

          -  Patients without national health insurance cover

          -  Pregnant or breast-feeding women

          -  allografts and autografts of Haematopoietic Stem Cells (HSC)
      </textblock>
